	* source/pthread/_context.s: Add PIC instructions and declare
	objects and functions for ELF DSO.
	* source/pthread/_yield.s: Likewise.
	* source/pthread/_ints.s: Likewise.
	* source/pthread/_exit.s: Likewise.

